{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC11_ELI_050.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x13,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hello, Elise."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Welcome, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Are you reading again?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yes, that's right."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "...Hey, I was wondering about this, but why do you like reading so much?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Well, I think it's because you can experience worlds that you don't know, some that you could never even imagine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "But I feel like you've read the same books over and over again..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hehe. Even if it's the same book, reading it at different times can lead to different impressions and thoughts."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "What do you mean?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "If you read a romance novel while in love, it can fuel your passion. But when things aren't going well, it can hurt..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Your feelings at the time of reading can change your impressions of a book like that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Are you in love with someone?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "That was just hypothetical."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Oh. I was a little excited for a moment."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Hehe. Also, when you read the same book two or three times, you can make new discoveries."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I know that feeling. It's especially true for really difficult books."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I get it now..."
        }
    ]
}